        <div class="body">
    	<div class="widget-carousel" data-items="2">
					<div class="widget-list-item">
		  		<h2 class="heading equalHeight"><a href="/news/2016-ct1-round-1-open-for-applications">2016 CT1 round 1 open for applications</a></h2>
	       		<div class="item-content"><p>As&nbsp;of 10am this morning Wednesday 9 November 2016, CT1 recruitment&nbsp;round&nbsp;1 is&nbsp;now open for applications through the&nbsp;Oriel website!
The window for applications closes on&nbsp; <a href="/news/2016-ct1-round-1-open-for-applications" class="more">Read More <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></a></p></div>		  	</div>

					<div class="widget-list-item">
		  		<h2 class="heading equalHeight"><a href="/news/ct1-recruitment-website-updated-for-2017">CT1 Recruitment website updated for 2017</a></h2>
