		  		<h2 class="heading equalHeight"><a href="/news/removal-of-the-18-months-experience-rule">Removal of the 18 months experience rule</a></h2>
	       		<div class="item-content"><p>In previous recruitment years there has been a rule that you cannot apply to CT1 posts in CMT/ACCS-AM if you have 18 months or more experience in medical specialties at a level above foundation or equ <a href="/news/removal-of-the-18-months-experience-rule" class="more">Read More <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></a></p></div>		  	</div>

